text:
ねぇママ
ここで何
してるの?
style: font-size: 14px;color: black;background-color: white;left: 66.41%;top: 2.99%;width: 9.19%;height: 7.71%;text-align: center;display: flex;flex-direction: column;align-items: center;justify-content: center;border-radius: 50%;font-weight: normal;

text:
お昼よ。
アンタは何よ?
style: font-size: 14px;color: black;background-color: white;left: 78.34%;top: 3.66%;width: 10.98%;height: 8.30%;text-align: center;display: flex;flex-direction: column;align-items: center;justify-content: center;border-radius: 50%;font-weight: normal;

text:
一日中寝てると
お姉ちゃんみたく
落ちこぼれるわよ
style: font-size: 14px;color: black;background-color: white;left: 11.52%;top: 33.25%;width: 15.51%;height: 8.55%;text-align: center;display: flex;flex-direction: column;align-items: center;justify-content: center;border-radius: 50%;font-weight: normal;

font-size: 18px;color: black;background-color: white;left: 31.68%;top: 39.03%;width: 9.67%;height: 4.69%;text-align: center;display: flex;flex-direction: column;align-items: center;justify-content: center;border-radius: 50%;font-weight: normal;

text:
オレは
落ちこぼれて
ねぇよ。
オレ達は学校が
直るまで休校
style: font-size: 14px;color: black;background-color: white;left: 47.08%;top: 33.08%;width: 13.25%;height: 10.39%;text-align: center;display: flex;flex-direction: column;align-items: center;justify-content: center;border-radius: 50%;font-weight: normal;

text:
言っとくけど
私は一日中
寝てない
style: font-size: 14px;color: black;background-color: white;left: 83.00%;top: 35.01%;width: 11.93%;height: 6.54%;text-align: center;display: flex;flex-direction: column;align-items: center;justify-content: center;border-radius: 50%;font-weight: normal;

text:
朝起きて
すぐ化粧
してるし
style: font-size: 14px;color: black;background-color: white;left: 83.11%;top: 41.04%;width: 12.29%;height: 7.80%;text-align: center;display: flex;flex-direction: column;align-items: center;justify-content: center;border-radius: 50%;font-weight: normal;

text:
変態のガキ
みたいな
露出趣味も
無いの
style: font-size: 14px;color: black;background-color: white;left: 46.96%;top: 51.69%;width: 12.65%;height: 9.22%;text-align: center;display: flex;flex-direction: column;align-items: center;justify-content: center;border-radius: 50%;font-weight: normal;

text:
地獄へ
落ちろ
ニクシー

text:
もう行くわ
コレ
あなたに
style: font-size: 14px;color: black;background-color: white;left: 16.89%;top: 68.05%;width: 11.22%;height: 6.96%;text-align: center;display: flex;flex-direction: column;align-items: center;justify-content: center;border-radius: 50%;font-weight: normal;

text:
パパは
忙しいから
大切なお客に
渡してって
